title: The Maxx new video old audio
description:
These are The Maxx episodes that were ripped from the DVD release of the show, except i have repaired the episodes using the old audio from the previous editions that were available.  

I also recreated the cut video clips using fantastically cheap techniques.

So, the episodes are DVD quality with "I wanna marry a lighthouse keeper" restored, and the old music for the scene where Maxx is chasing the Is restored, and a ton of other little changes that really pissed me off about the new release.

Enjoy.
